# Server / data hotspots

- Plan reads → `src/lib/plans.ts` only (`published:true`). Never raw `prisma.plan` in pages.
- `public-routes.ts` = allowlist. New private route → `NEVER_CACHE_PREFIXES` + `tests/offline.test.ts`.
- Identity from session only (`getCurrentUser`/`requireUser`). No client `userId`.
- Actions: never throw; `guardAction`; `formInt` bounded; `safeReturnTo`; rate-limit returns bool.
- Uploads only `storage.ts`. New image host → `img-src` AND `images.remotePatterns`.
- `DATABASE_URL` pooled + `DIRECT_URL` direct, same DB. Keep `check-db-urls.mjs`. No `buildCommand` in `vercel.json`.
- Public cost = tiers `$`…`$$$$$` only. No `formatCents` / dollar UI.
- `PlanView` has no `userId`; log views client-side only.
